{"tid":985864,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"馬英九稱九二共識是仙丹 游錫堃：你去香港住一年給我們看","createTime":"2019-01-18T03:46:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-18T08:40:10.000Z","uid":5195,"like":148,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"b518d654ff3f6fd2f53538cbfad30dcdc1f9fa0c","tid":985864,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T03:46:13.000Z","msg":"〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕前總統馬英九昨接受廣播節目專訪，重申九二共識確實存在，更稱九二共識是「保命仙丹」，對此，前行政院長游錫堃在臉書上向馬英九喊話：「馬先生，請你回去你的出生地，『一國兩制的香港』，住一年給我們看看吧！」<br />\n游錫堃直言，「只要回去住一年就好」，回去一國兩制的香港住給大家看看，不然就不要騙台灣人了，台灣人已經不像以前那麼好騙了。"},{"pid":"b66d0590654827b7786b5f7d8935de24a63cfbe7","tid":985864,"uid":121146,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T03:47:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 叫佢黎唱一次國歌"},{"pid":"c0c91e313490c4ad47d58e168ad3302b213e8e95","tid":985864,"uid":46947,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T03:52:36.000Z","msg":"嚟到記住用四五佰萬買間150尺劏房屋住一年。"},{"pid":"78234763c4f4a000516c84b9418016f386af519b","tid":985864,"uid":35790,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"quote":{"pid":"b66d0590654827b7786b5f7d8935de24a63cfbe7","tid":985864,"uid":121146,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T03:47:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 叫佢黎唱一次國歌"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T03:53:10.000Z","msg":"對佢來講有問題咩？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8455e1feff6b08a796d8f45ba166f0f1d19e842","tid":985864,"uid":115525,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"quote":{"pid":"b66d0590654827b7786b5f7d8935de24a63cfbe7","tid":985864,"uid":121146,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T03:47:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 叫佢黎唱一次國歌"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T03:55:02.000Z","msg":"叫佢黎唱一次國歌<br />\n要求所有新聞 正名 「國立臺灣大學」<br />\n用順豐寄書黎香港<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal